Codex of Research and Test Reactor Docket Numbers

Source: R/dockets.R
RTR_docket_codex.Rd

Docket numbers are hard to keep track of so let nrcadams keep track of them for you! This exported tibble provides the project name, and docket number for a selection of RTRs

Usage

RTR_docket_codex

Format

A tibble with columns for project names, docket numbers.

Value

tibble of docket numbers

Examples

nrcadams::docket_codex
#> # A tibble: 31 × 4
#>    Project                         Company                    DocketNumber NLWR 
#>    <chr>                           <chr>                             <dbl> <lgl>
#>  1 MSRR Pre-Application            ACU                            99902088 TRUE 
#>  2 MSRR Part 50                    ACU                             5000610 TRUE
